{"tid":279693,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[scuba]召喚今個暑假想學潛水既巴絲","createTime":"2017-06-11T13:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T07:39:39.000Z","uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"528f6891166b2ee61edf9c0d4dbf96a81590325b","tid":279693,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:01:09.000Z","msg":"黎緊7/8月諗住學scuba diving<br />\n先利申定先:絕非廣告/打手<br />\n搵到間叫:海浪潮音(<a href=\"http://www.sounds-oceans.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sounds-oceans.com%2F&d=aEUrblTqWL9m2n5lRtb41mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d44d0bf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sounds-oceans.com/</a>)<br />\n學既system會係:naui<br />\n價錢方面,o仔會係$3580,a仔會係$2680<br />\no+a就係$5800<br />\n直接出海兩次,無泳池堂,包哂所有野<br />\n出海地點會係大浦三門仔<br />\n但是呢,我就得一個人,咁如果自己一個去學呢,就可能要同d街人一齊上<br />\n所以就想係到睇下有無巴絲有興趣想一齊學,咁就可以大家互就時間<br />\n有興趣既巴絲可以add我telgram<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd931c74867688b6c3792bcd1539c355a3ed5de","tid":279693,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T13:23:15.000Z","msg":"十連無難度"},{"pid":"5b144ee2af61e977d6ff9c29149a981dea1594a3","tid":279693,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"2連"},{"pid":"1ea6356bcce78227bdb6a07ff18f64a2906cd541","tid":279693,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:42:23.000Z","msg":"3連"},{"pid":"135eaf13d39702a33859b5cd4afcd6709f1f1a05","tid":279693,"uid":107990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"留明！"},{"pid":"b68d835b0bb104f2c0fd7317710531a6bfaf59d6","tid":279693,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明！</blockquote><br />\n巴打有興趣既可以telgram我wor<br />\nbtw,臨訓前再次挑戰十連"},{"pid":"c5b76f74b564edfb03a40751361ed5424bc09613","tid":279693,"uid":77910,"like":0,"dislike"